<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:11:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>北京称马尔代夫总统将于1月8日至12日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/president-maldives-visit-china-jan-8-12-beijing-says-2024-01-05/</link><description>中国外交部周五在声明中表示，马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖将于 1 月 8 日至 12 日对中国进行国事访问，这将是对该岛国巨大邻国印度的高调冷落。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 13:48:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/president-maldives-visit-china-jan-8-12-beijing-says-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>行业专家对中国对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查做出回应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/industry-experts-react-chinas-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-brandy-2024-01-05/</link><description>中国周五对从欧盟进口的白兰地发起反倾销调查，调查重点是200升（44英国加仑）以下容器的白兰地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 13:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/industry-experts-react-chinas-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-brandy-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>王毅：中美合作“不再是一种选择……而是势在必行”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-us-cooperation-no-longer-optional-imperative-both-world-wang-yi-2024-01-05/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周五表示，中美关系最紧迫的任务是双方建立正确的理解与合作，并强调这对世界“不再是一种选择……而是势在必行”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 11:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-us-cooperation-no-longer-optional-imperative-both-world-wang-yi-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国财富管理公司中植申请破产清算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-court-accepts-wealth-manager-zhongzhis-bankruptcy-application-2024-01-05/</link><description>中国财富管理公司中植企业集团因未能偿还债务而申请破产清算，该公司正努力应对房地产市场日益低迷的局面。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-court-accepts-wealth-manager-zhongzhis-bankruptcy-application-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>贝莱德任命范华接替唐朝为中国区总裁 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/blackrock-appoints-hua-fan-head-china-succeeding-tony-tang-sources-2024-01-05/</link><description>两名知情人士称，贝莱德公司已任命其控股的中国资产管理部门前总经理范华为中国区负责人。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:12:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/blackrock-appoints-hua-fan-head-china-succeeding-tony-tang-sources-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>童话般的冰雕吸引大批游客来到中国哈尔滨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fairy-tale-ice-sculptures-lure-droves-tourists-into-chinas-harbin-2024-01-05/</link><description>中国一年一度的冰雪节上周五开幕，童话般的冰雕吸引了大批游客，他们小心翼翼地在光滑的冰雪上拖行，拖着孩子乘坐雪橇在公园里转悠。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 08:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fairy-tale-ice-sculptures-lure-droves-tourists-into-chinas-harbin-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构称特斯拉将在中国维修 162 万辆汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-162-mln-vehicles-china-regulator-2024-01-05/</link><description>市场监管机构周五表示，特斯拉正在中国有效召回 162 万辆汽车，包括其 S、X、3 和 Y 车型。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-162-mln-vehicles-china-regulator-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>赛默飞停止在西藏销售法医技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/thermo-fisher-halts-forensic-tech-sales-tibet-2024-01-05/</link><description>赛默飞世尔科技发言人表示，该公司已承诺停止在西藏销售可用于识别个人身份的法医技术和设备。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/thermo-fisher-halts-forensic-tech-sales-tibet-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾国家安全顾问对中国外交保持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-remains-open-diplomatic-discussions-with-china-national-security-2024-01-05/</link><description>菲律宾国家安全顾问周五在一份声明中表示，菲律宾仍然对与中国进行外交讨论持开放态度，并相信两国可以通过和平对话解决南海争端。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 06:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-remains-open-diplomatic-discussions-with-china-national-security-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国推动股票基金推出以支持股市 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pushes-equity-fund-launches-support-stock-market-sources-2024-01-05/</link><description>四位直接了解此事的消息人士称，随着当局忙于重振落后的股市，北京已非正式地要求中国的一些基金管理公司优先推出股票基金，而不是债券基金等其他产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 06:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pushes-equity-fund-launches-support-stock-market-sources-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年初台湾选举对美国稳定与中国关系的目标构成考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-election-poses-early-2024-test-us-aim-steady-china-ties-2024-01-05/</link><description>台湾下周的选举无论谁获胜都会给华盛顿带来挑战，执政党的胜利肯定会加剧与中国的紧张关系，而反对派的胜利可能会引发有关台湾国防政策的尴尬问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 05:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-election-poses-early-2024-test-us-aim-steady-china-ties-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜向韩国军事“歹徒”海上发射炮火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/skorea-orders-evacuation-island-near-north-korea-border-2024-01-05/</link><description>朝鲜周五在与韩国有争议的海上边界附近发射了 200 多发炮弹，两国之间的紧张局势再次升级，并促使韩国采取“相应”行动，进行实弹演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:40:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/skorea-orders-evacuation-island-near-north-korea-border-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉凭借实时策略在中国销售效率超越比亚迪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-trumps-byd-china-sales-efficiency-with-real-time-strategy-2024-01-05/</link><description>据三名知情人士透露，特斯拉在中国的战略是对销售人员进行实时、积极的管理，这使其门店比在全球最大汽车市场上销售比亚迪和其他品牌的经销商更具优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-trumps-byd-china-sales-efficiency-with-real-time-strategy-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>议员要求五角大楼考虑禁止美国投资中国移远通信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-ask-pentagon-consider-barring-us-investments-chinas-quectel-2024-01-04/</link><description>美国众议院中国委员会的共和党和民主党最高领导人周四要求拜登政府考虑将中国移远无线公司列入中国军工企业名单。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-ask-pentagon-consider-barring-us-investments-chinas-quectel-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>香港大亨律师就证人酷刑指控向联合国提出上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-tycoons-lawyers-appeal-un-over-witness-torture-accusation-2024-01-04/</link><description>香港民主大亨黎智英的律师周四表示，他们已就一名证人在提供定罪证据之前受到酷刑的待遇问题向联合国酷刑问题专家提出上诉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-tycoons-lawyers-appeal-un-over-witness-torture-accusation-2024-01-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>